| Month | Subscription Rate | Campaign Volume | Interpretation |
|-------|-------------------|-----------------|----------------|
| March | 47.3% | Low | High efficiency, low volume |
| December | 42.1% | Medium | Holiday season effectiveness |
| October | 38.2% | Medium | Fall campaign sweet spot |
